data.description: This Charming and inviting 2 story home is in the Green Valley Ranch community! Enjoy the bright and open living room that leads into the dining and kitchen area upon entry. Located in the kitchen are upgraded 42-inch kitchen cabinets and stainless-steel appliances. New interior paint and carpet throughout. This home features 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, and one loft that could be easily converted to a 3rd bedroom. Great location, minutes from community parks and schools, shopping, restaurants, and easy access to major routes and DIA.
